Key Match Events: Ishan Kishan scored 89 runs off 56 balls, including 10 fours and 3 sixes.
Post-Match Reflections: Ishan Kishan was named the Player of the Match.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at the Bharat Ratna Shri Atal Bihari Vajpayee Ekana Cricket Stadium in Lucknow.
Others: The match was the first T20I for Deepak Hooda.
